tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ChatbotDialogueHistories (
    dialog_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    bot_id UUID NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    message TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE chatbot_dialogues (
    dialogue_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    message TEXT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES chatbot_users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE dialogues (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    bot_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    message TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE dialogues (
  dialogue_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  agent_id UUID,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  message TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE conversations (
  conversation_id UUID  PRIMARY KEY,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  dialogue_id UUID,
  user_id UUID,
  agent_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE user_messages (
    message_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    sender TEXT,
    message TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE conversations (
    conversation_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    bot_id INT,
    start_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    end_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    duration INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE conversation_messages (
    message_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    conversation_id INT,
    sender TEXT,
    message TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
